OpenAMRobot Platform Software

This repository is part of the OpenAMRobot open-source robotics ecosystem.

Project:
OpenAMRobot — Affordable Open Autonomous Mobile Robot Platform

Organization:
https://github.com/openAMRobot

Website:
https://botshare.ai

Purpose:
This repository contains ROS 2 software, simulation, navigation,
autodocking, control, drivers, tooling, and related infrastructure for
the OpenAMRobot platform.

The project aims to support:
- affordable robotics development
- robotics education
- research and prototyping
- SME automation
- open-source collaboration
- modular robotics ecosystems

Important notice:
This repository may include experimental robotics software and simulation
components. Users are responsible for validating safety, reliability,
and compliance before deploying software on physical robotic systems.

The software is provided for educational, research, prototyping,
and development purposes.

